highlights.text: “WOAHH (feat. Clarent)” by Rvssian, Young Miko, Omar Courtz, and Clarent is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Spain, up 35 spots at #115.
Beéle has the most spots on Top Songs Spain. “La Plena - W Sound 05” is the highest at #2.
